data.description: Attention Investors! This property offers incredible potential for renovation and expansion. The current owner began a remodel that needs to be completed on the inside, particularly in the basement, which is not included in the 3052 square feet of this 2-story home. When fully finished, the home is projected to exceed 4500 square feet, offering a substantial increase in living space. While not move-in ready, the home can be purchased at $475,000 with a credit to complete the renovations needed - OR - can be purchased as-is for $415,000! The floor plan includes a spacious master suite, formal dining room, eat-in kitchen, laundry room, and double car garage on the main level. Upstairs, there are four oversized bedrooms and a loft. The basement, constructed with 6" ICF technology, offers potential for a full bathroom and features a FEMA-approved safe room. Perched on a hill, this home is not at risk of flooding and is an excellent candidate for solar power. This is your chance to make this property into a truly remarkable home!
